<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <title>Recipe Search</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/style.css">
    <style>
       
        li{
            font-size: 13.5px;
            list-style: none;
            margin: 6px;
        }
        .about{
            width: 300px;
        }
         @media (max-width: 720px) {
            .text {
            display: none;
            }
             .about{
            width: 100%;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body class="index">
    <div class="main">
        <h1 style="text-align: center; font-size: 60px; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 10px; 	
            color: #fff; background-color: rgba(17, 25, 40, 0.75);
    backdrop-filter: blur(1px) saturate(180%); padding: 1px 10px; border-radius: 3px;">
            \/𝓮𝓰𝓲e P𝓪𝓻𝓪𝓭𝓲𝓬e  
        </h1>
        <form action="/results" method="get" style="display: flex; justify-content: center; align-items: center; flex-wrap: wrap; margin: 0px 5px;">
            <input class="input" type="text" placeholder="Ingredients / Dishes" id="ingredients" name="ingredients" required>
            <button type="submit" style="background-color: #85e56d; border: 1px solid #4CAF50; color: #ffffff; border-radius: 8px; padding: 10px 20px; font-size: 16px; cursor: pointer; margin: 4px 4px;">
                Search
            </button>

        </form>
        <div class="text" style="color: white; text-align: center; font-size: 18px; margin: 0 5px; font-family: 'Times New Roman', Times, serif;">
            <p>Your one-stop destination for discovering delicious recipes based on the ingredients you have at home!</p>
            <p>Whether you're looking to create a quick meal with what’s in your pantry or explore new culinary adventures, Recipe Finder is here to help you find the perfect dish.</p>
            <p>Simply enter the ingredients you have, and we'll suggest recipes tailored just for you—saving time, reducing waste, and adding variety to your meals.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
    <h2>Try our top rated Recipes across INDIA</h2>
    <div class="recepie">
        <% if (recipes && recipes.length > 0) { %>
            <% recipes.forEach(recipe => { %>
                <div class="container">
                    <a class="align" href="/recipe/<%= encodeURIComponent(recipe.title) %>?url=<%= encodeURIComponent(recipe.link) %>">
                        <img class="image_show image" src="<%= recipe.image %>" alt="<%= recipe.title %>">
                        <h3><%= recipe.title %></h3>
                    </a>
                    <!-- <img class="image_show" src="<%= recipe.image %>" alt="<%= recipe.title %>" style="width:200px;height:auto;"> -->
                    <!-- <p><%= recipe.description %></p> -->
                    <p><strong>Last updated:</strong> <%= recipe.updated %></p>
                </div>
            <% }); %>
        <% } else if (typeof recipes !== "undefined") { %> <!-- If no recipes found -->
            <li>No recipes found for the given ingredients.</li>
        <% } %>
        </div>


        <!------------------------- footer------------------------ -->
        <footer class="footer" style=" background-color: #313232;
background-image: linear-gradient(135deg, #383e41 0%, #3e3e3f 100%);
 height: fit-content; display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; flex-wrap: wrap;">

            <div style=" height: fit-content; display: flex; flex-direction: row; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; flex-wrap: wrap; border-bottom: 2px solid rgb(81, 76, 76); padding-bottom: 20px;">
                <div class="about" style="display: flex; align-items: center; flex-direction: column; margin: 14px; padding: 15px 25px; color: #ffffff; border-right: 2px solid rgb(81, 76, 76);">
                    <h4>About site</h4>
                     <p style="font-size: 14px;">Discover a variety of delicious recipes tailored to the ingredients you have on hand. Our goal is to make cooking easy, fun, and accessible for everyone!</p>
                </div>
                <div class="about" style="display: flex; align-items: center; flex-direction: column; margin: 14px; padding: 15px; color: #ffffff; border-right: 2px solid rgb(81, 76, 76);">
                    <h4>Products</h4>
                    <li>Recipes</li>
                    <li>Ingredients</li>
                    <li>Prepration</li>
                    <li>Nutrition</li>
                </div>
                <div class="about" style="display: flex; align-items: center; flex-direction: column; margin: 14px; padding: 15px; color: #ffffff; border-right: 2px solid rgb(81, 76, 76);">
                    <h4>Contact</h4>
                    <li>Noida, Uttar Pradesh</li>
                    <li>Hrajz.work@gmail.com</li>
                    <li>+9170****085*</li>
                    <li>+917485***81*</li>
                </div>
                <div class="about" style="display: flex; align-items: center; flex-direction: column; margin: 14px; padding: 15px; color: #ffffff;">
                    <h4>Follow us on</h4>
                    <li>Instagram</li>
                    <li>Twitter</li>
                    <li>Linkedin</li>
                    <li>Github</li>
                    <li>Leetcode</li>
                </div>
            </div>
            <p style="background-color: #090909; width: 100%; margin: 0; color: white; padding: 20px 0; text-align: center;"></div>
                   © 2024 copyright : Vegieparadice.com
            </p>
          
        </footer>
        
        

</body>

</html>